### Mr. Johnson Subedi

youth-initiative-p

Mr. Johnson Subedi is a 18 year old young Technopreneur from Parbat. He is co-founder of  AuraED, a non-profit organization, which focuses on spreading digital literacy all over Nepal by interacting with the underprivileged kids physically and teaching them different aspects of technology. Currently, He is working as a python programming intern at Bloom Nepal. He animate the visualizations of the contents of the academics which is helping students(with low facility) in Bloom Nepal school to understand the content clearly and visually. [...] Apart from that, He is also working on his own research about improving the Nepalese share market by using technology like Blockchain and smart contracts which helps to improve transparency in the market, cut off intermediaries, reduces costs and commissions to invest in the market and also reduces market manipulation.

## GLOCAL'S 20UNDER20

Glocal’s 20 under 20 is an umbrella title for 20 early change makers, who are teenagers from diverse fields, stepping out to create an impact in the society. Glocal is dedicated in recognizing these teenager’s initiative, achievement naming 20 Under 20. [...] These 20 youths below 20 years of age are the game-changers who have done something worth an inspiration in their life. Glocal’s ‘20 under 20’ aims to recognize these enthusiastic young souls who have the vision to do something ordinary in the most extra-ordinary way possible. We believe in their dreams and want to acknowledge these diverse talents who hold the potential to be the change-makers and the future leaders.

# Glocal announces 20under20 for 10th edition of Glocal Teen Hero

B360
Glocal announces 20under20 for 10th edition of Glocal Teen Hero

KATHMANDU: Glocal has revealed its 20under20 list for the 10th edition, celebrating 20 remarkable and influential Nepali teenagers under the age of 20. This prestigious title honours early change-makers from diverse fields who are making a positive impact on society.

For a decade, the Glocal Teen Hero initiative has recognised teenagers who excel beyond academics, providing a platform to showcase their extraordinary talents. Glocal Teen Hero Nepal acknowledges teenagers’ initiation, creativity, and enthusiasm, empowering them to catalyse positive change at the intersection of global and local domains.
